		<h1>Dental Cleaning & Exam in Surrey: Preventive Care for a Healthy Smile</h1>
		<p class="intro">
			Preventive care is the absolute foundation of long-term oral health. Even with diligent daily brushing and flossing, plaque and tartar can accumulate in hard-to-reach areas. At Canary Dental in Surrey, our gentle dental cleanings and thorough comprehensive exams are designed to help you avoid painful cavities, reverse early gum disease (gingivitis), and keep your teeth bright, strong, and healthy for life.
		</p>
